sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant HospitalWorkloadSimulator as Hospital Workload Simulator
    participant ThresholdScaler
    participant RLAgent as RL Agent (PPO)
    participant Cloud as Cloud (AWS)

    User->>HospitalWorkloadSimulator: Generate hospital CPU workload data
    HospitalWorkloadSimulator->>ThresholdScaler: Provide workload data
    ThresholdScaler->>Cloud: Simulate threshold-based scaling
    ThresholdScaler->>User: Output baseline results (SLA, cost, VMs)
    HospitalWorkloadSimulator->>RLAgent: Provide workload data
    RLAgent->>Cloud: Train RL agent for scaling
    RLAgent->>User: Output RL results (SLA, cost, VMs)
    User->>User: Compare RL vs Threshold results
